          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0354P1-05548'>
        <a name='S6CV0354P1_20000725_WH_35'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-luff' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
